                Brindisi HAMBURG<lb/>F.<lb/>210<lb/>72<lb/>N 5-6N 1<lb/>Messrs.<lb/>L. Kniffler
                &amp; Co<lb/>P. D.<lb/>Yokohama<lb/>Japan<lb/>⟨1872<lb/>Hamburg 2nd October<lb/>H,C,
                Bock<lb/>R[eceived] 2nd Nov.<lb/>16th Dec.<lb/>KC⟩</p>
